<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Objection" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Objection,</orth> criminal charge, accusation, reproach: <cit><quote>you do not well to bear with their perverse --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.129" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 129</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your spiteful false --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.158" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 158</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I dare your worst --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.307" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 307</bibl></cit>. cf. the verb <emph>object</emph> in <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 28</bibl> and <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 7</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>